<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.9.5">
<l>vantāyeṉ maṉattē; vantunī pukuntapiṉṉai</l>
<l>yentāypō yaṟiyā yituvē yamaiyātō</l>
<l>kontārpaim poḻilcūḻ kuṭantaik kiṭantukanta</l>
<l>maintāvuṉ ṉaiyeṉṟum maṟavāmaip peṟṟēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You came into my heart; after you came and entered [there],</l>
<l>My father, you do not consider going. Isn’t this enough?</l>
<l>Young one who is happy sleeping in Kuṭantai encircled by fresh groves</l>
<l>Filled with [flower] clusters, I [also] attained daily not forgetting you!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
